### GET ALL GAMES
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games

###

### GET ONE GAME
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/1

###

### GET NON-EXISTING GAME
GET http://localhost:8080/api/games/999

###

### CREATE NEW GAME
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cyberpunk 2077",
  "platform": "PC",
  "price": 59.99,
  "seller": "CD Projekt RED"
}

###

### CREATE ANOTHER GAME
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Elden Ring",
  "platform": "PlayStation 5",
  "price": 69.99,
  "seller": "FromSoftware"
}

###

### UPDATE EXISTING GAME
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/games/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt - Complete Edition",
  "platform": "PC",
  "price": 39.99,
  "seller": "CD Projekt RED"
}

###

### UPDATE NON-EXISTING GAME
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/games/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ghost Game",
  "platform": "PC",
  "price": 0.01,
  "seller": "Nobody"
}

###

### DELETE EXISTING GAME
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/games/2

###

### DELETE NON-EXISTING GAME
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/games/999

###

### CREATE GAME WITH INVALID DATA (empty title)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "platform": "PC",
  "price": 29.99,
  "seller": "Test Seller"
}

###

### CREATE GAME WITH INVALID DATA (negative price)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Game",
  "platform": "Xbox",
  "price": -10.00,
  "seller": "Test Seller"
}

